title: Vanilla Ice Goes Amish - Season 1 Complete
description:
Vanilla Ice Goes Amish - Season 1 Complete




Pop icon and knock-out home renovator Vanilla Ice ditches his high tech power tools and moves to Amish country to learn the lost art of hand craftsmanship. Go inside the largest Amish settlement in the U.S. as a group of young men and women help him tackle construction projects ranging from kitchen additions to traditional barn raisings Ã¢â‚¬â€ all without nails and screws. He'll earn his keep working on the farm as he learns to embrace the simpler life and become fully immersed in the unique culture that has been isolated from the rest of the world.
